        <p>NAD⁺ fuels the enzymes that patch damaged DNA and clear worn-out cells. As it declines, that daily maintenance falls behind.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="prob-card">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="8"/><path d="M12 8v4l3 2"/></svg>
        <h3>Cells age faster</h3>
        <p>With less NAD⁺, the systems that keep cells youthful and resilient lose momentum — and the effect compounds with every passing year.</p>
