      <h2>Before you start.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="reveal">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">What is NMN, and why not just take NAD⁺? <span class="plus">+</span></div>
        <div class="faq-a">NAD⁺ is poorly absorbed when taken orally. NMN (Nicotinamide Mononucleotide) is a direct precursor your body readily converts into NAD⁺ — which is why it's the preferred delivery route.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">How long until I notice a difference? <span class="plus">+</span></div>
        <div class="faq-a">Most people take NMN+ daily for 4–8 weeks before evaluating effects, since replenishing cellular NAD⁺ is a gradual process. Consistency matters more than any single dose.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">Is it third-party tested? <span class="plus">+</span></div>
        <div class="faq-a">Yes. Every batch is tested by an independent lab for purity and potency before release. Certificates of Analysis are available on request.</div>
