      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">Can I cancel my subscription? <span class="plus">+</span></div>
        <div class="faq-a">Anytime — no fees, no minimum commitment. Manage, pause, or cancel directly from your account dashboard.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">Is NMN safe? <span class="plus">+</span></div>
        <div class="faq-a">NMN has been generally well tolerated in published human studies at doses comparable to ours. Supplements aren't right for everyone, though — talk to your healthcare provider before starting, especially if you're pregnant, nursing, taking medication, or managing a condition.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">Why UTHEVER® NMN specifically? <span class="plus">+</span></div>
        <div class="faq-a">UTHEVER® is one of the few NMN ingredients evaluated in a published randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled human trial. We'd rather build on an ingredient with public evidence than an unbranded powder.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
